queries.sql:
select * , tf.firm as firmname, tp.position as pos
        from tbl_users as tu,tbl_firm as tf, tbl_position as tp
        where BINARY email = 'daviesjohn234567@gmail.com' 
        and tu.firm = tf.firmID
        and tu.position = tp.posID
